title: Queen Wilhelmina of The Netherlands in exile Londen

sources.title: Queen Wilhelmina of The Netherlands in exile Londen
sources.description: Queen Wilhelmina of The Netherlands in exile in Londen during WW-II. She was not the only royal in exile in London when these royals visited King George VI and his wife at Buckigham Palace. Software-enhanced and artificially colored film. Source B&W footage: Beeld en Geluid
